# HR System - Talent Acquisition & Workforce Entry

## Core Modules

### 1. Applicant Management (Candidate Facing)
- **Careers Page/Job Board** - Public job listings for all positions
- **Application Form** - Submit resume, contact info, cover letter
- **Application Tracking** - View status: Under Review → Interview → Offer → Hired

### 2. Recruitment Management (HR Admin Facing)
- **Job Posting Manager** - Create, edit, close positions
- **Kanban Pipeline** - Drag-drop applicants through stages: Screening → Interview → Hired → Rejected
- **Interview Scheduling** - Schedule and manage interview notes

### 3. New Hire Onboarding
- **Digital Checklist** - Automated onboarding tasks for new employees
- **Task Tracking** - Contract signing, uniform, training completion

### 4. Performance Management
- **30-60-90 Day Reviews** - Probationary period evaluations
- **Skill Assessments** - Role-specific competency tracking

### 5. Social Recognition
- **Welcome Wall** - New hire introductions to team
- **Kudos System** - Recognition badges and team morale

## User Roles

| Role | Permissions |
|------|------------|
| **Applicant** | View jobs, apply, track own status |
| **HR Admin** | Manage jobs, review candidates, control pipeline, onboarding |

